videos.description: UCLA's Bolu Olorunfunmi fumbles behind the line of scrimmage and Cal's Jordan Kunaszyk falls on the ball at the UCLA 17-yard line to complete the turnover, setting up a Golden Bears field goal.
videos.headline: Golden Bears recover fumble deep in Bruins' territory

videos.description: Bruins QB Josh Rosen drops back and connects with Theo Howard in the front of the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown, giving UCLA a 7-3 lead.
videos.headline: Rosen finds Howard in the end zone for UCLA score

videos.description: Bruins RB Brandon Stephens breaks free along the right sideline for a 37-yard pickup, getting all the way down to the Cal 12-yard line and setting up a UCLA field goal.
videos.headline: UCLA's Stephens bursts out of the backfield

videos.description: Josh Rosen throws it where only his receiver could get it, tossing a strike to Jordan Lasley in the end zone for a 17-yard score, putting UCLA ahead 17-6.
videos.headline: Rosen tosses perfect back-shoulder pass for Bruins TD

videos.description: UCLA QB Josh Rosen feels the pressure in the pocket and gets tackled by Alex Funches who tears the back of Rosen's jersey in the process. Rosen would not play in the second half.
videos.headline: Rosen knocked out of game after big hit, causing jersey to rip

videos.description: Golden Bears QB Ross Bowers fakes a handoff and keeps the ball himself, scoring from two yards out for a score.
videos.headline: Bowers scrambles in for Cal TD

videos.description: Ross Bowers lofts a pass to the end zone and Jordan Veasy jumps up and comes down with it for a 6-yard score, tying the game at 27-27.
videos.headline: Golden Bears tie it up as Veasy wins jump ball in end zone

videos.description: Bruins kicker JJ Molson kicks a 37-yard field goal with four seconds left on the clock to give UCLA a 30-27 win.
videos.headline: UCLA nails field goal in closing seconds to seal win over Cal
